text: "Club Tropicana" is a 1983 song by English pop duo Wham! and is the fifth and final single from their debut studio album Fantastic. It went to number 4 in Ireland and in the United Kingdom, number 8 in the Netherlands, number 10 in Norway and number 13 in Germany. == References == Category:1983 songs Category:Wham! songs
title: Club Tropicana
